{"tid":55710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想戒煙 有無過來人比心得","createTime":"2016-12-26T15:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T15:54:33.000Z","uid":41813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50f689d484f39351896d9cf37829a9ca6a03040f","tid":55710,"uid":41813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:25:22.000Z","msg":"煙齡三年<br />\n每日食五支左右<br />\n食緊五號煙<br />\nFinal或好多野做就會食好多<br />\n有無巴打戒到可以比建議小弟"},{"pid":"e8ec69b08c60c5e883e47efd7a875a88b5c63095","tid":55710,"uid":14476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:29:18.000Z","msg":"8至10年煙齡，一日包半，戒左2年完全無食，好睇決心，戒左第三次先成功戒到，之前兩次都係一個月無食之後失敗，同埋少啲落酒吧。"},{"pid":"7c27b2d1cac761b749f8b9e1557eada558cba1e9","tid":55710,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"4至5年煙齡<br />\n每1日至少1包<br />\n戒左接近兩年<br />\n其實無乜心得<br />\n死頂唔好食就得<br />\n當你想食嗰陣<br />\n咪搵其他野咬下eg.香口膠<br />\n頭一個禮拜最難頂<br />\n過左就無乜野<br />\n你一日食得嗰5枝<br />\n咁條癮都唔係好深姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a487762998e31ef1a7589f91a5ab7c73e01dda89","tid":55710,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"唔想食就自然唔食<br />\n我都唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}